<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE PRECIOUS BLOOD OF THE CROSS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kross-a chun thisan lun a um,
 Kross thiengtho chu ka mui;
 Thisan chu Isun ei hetsak,
 Keidi'n ma a luong ka.

[V2]
 Aw, thisan lopipen chuh,
 Isun A thawkna chuh;
 Kross chungah thisan lun aluong,
 Ginna'n ka na mu tai.

[V3]
 2. Kross chu, aw Kross giktak mai chuh,
 Isu'n kei din A pu'i;
 Lungkham taka A thawkna chuh,
 Kalvari-ah A ngai.

[V4]
 3. A zang em, Kross lul takmai chuh,
 Kross chuh ka vak thil a;
 Kenle ka pukang zo dei mawh,
 Bawl ingka Kraun um chuh.

[V5]
 4. Lallukhuk lopi pen mai chuh,
 Galhat lallukhuk chuh;
 Vanah Isu ka muh tieng leh,
 Ken le ziechuh khu'ng ka.

[V6]
 5. Ka mitthitui pawt ta puona,
 Hehpih haihloh na ah;
 Khawvel apat ei puidawk in,
 Nawpna mun ei tunin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>122</hymn_number>
</song>